The paper discusses the use of AI models in clinical decision-making, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the importance of understanding and trusting the predictions of these models, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
